<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN"
    "http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd">
    <html>
        <head>
            <meta charset="utf-8">
        </head>
        <body>
            <h1>Gig booking reciept</h1>
            <p>
                Dear <%= @user.email %>, thank you for buying your tickets through Gigbanana, please find below the reciept of your purchase
            </p>
            <table border="0" cellspacing="5" cellpadding="5">
                <tr>
                    <th>Gig</th>
                    <th>Time</th>
                    <th>Cost</th>
                </tr>
                <% @items.each do |item| %>
                    <tr>
                        <td><%= item.gig.name %></td>
                        <td><%= item.gig.pretty_start %></td>
                        <td><%= number_to_currency(item.gig.price, unit: '£') %></td>
                    </tr>
                <% end %>
                <tr><td></td><td></td>
                    <td><%= number_to_currency(@total, unit: '£') %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <p>We hope you enjoy the gigs you have booked and hope you will book with us again.</p>

            <p>Kind Regards,<br>Gigbanana</p>
        </body>
    </html>
